{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2016-06-02T23:40:30-05:00"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/06-02-everyone-is-shouting","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If everyone is shouting then joining them only adds to the noise. The first person to shout gets a reward but each person after her gets less. It doesn’t add to impact or success but instead makes the world a little bit worse. It drives away anyone who is following closely — those who truly care about what you’re doing."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/06-02-everyone-is-shouting"]}],"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","kind":"article","sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"title":"Everyone Is Shouting","color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"platforms":[{"name":"Brunow","introducedAt":"2017.01.20"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"type":"topic","title":"Brunow","url":"\/documentation\/brunow","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have something in common with him — if you think it is ridiculous that he is talking about himself in the first person here, so does he.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2016":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2016","title":"2016","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016","abstract":[],"kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"kind":"article","type":"topic","tit